  m_text: 'WASD to move character


    When you get close to animal, if available,
    you will be prompted to control the animal''s animator.


    Then, stay close
    to the animal and use these controls to change animal''s animation.


    T animal
    walk, hold Left Shift to run

    Keyboard 1 animal eat

    Keyboard 2 animal
    attack

    Keyboard 3 animal die


    Pressing 1,2,3 again will turn the animator
    back to the idle state.'
